{lang-eng}Jayinchuvaadu devakumaarudu bhayamu
Chendaka yundudi sarvamu pogottaka
Swatantrinchu konunu sarva devuni vaakkide{/lang-eng}

{lang-tam}ஜெயங்கொள்ளுகிறவன் தேவகுமாரன்
பயமே கொள்ளாதிருப்பான்;
எல்லாம் சுதந்தரிப்பான் எதையுமே இழக்கான்
வல்லவர் வாக்கேதான்.{/lang-tam}

{lang-eng}Adi prema vidina Ephes sanghamaa adiye nee
Koratha jayinchina neevu jeeva phalamulanu
Priyamuga bhujiyinthuvu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Shrestathamagu Smurnaa sanghamaa shramalanu
Ne maruvan jayinchina neeku rendava maranamu
Bhayapadi haani cheyadu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Pergamu sabha nee bodhayu, thappudu maargamula
Nerugudun jayinchina marugaina mannaa
Krotha peru thellani raatinithun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Thuyathaira sabha nee shakhti nerugudun
Neebhayamula nerugudun jayinchina janulapai
Nadhikaara mithun vekuva chukka nithun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Saardis sabha nee chaavu ne nerugudu thwaralona
Stirapadumu jayinchina neeku thellani vastramu
Lichi ninnoppu kondunu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Priyamagu oh Philadelphia sanghamaa nee
Aashakyatha theliyun jayinchina stambhamugaa
Nunchi neeku kroththa naamamu nidudun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Lavodikeya sabha nee lakshanamula daurbhagyatha
Theliyun jayinchina ninnu simhaasanamuna
Naatho koorchunda nithun{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Jayamondu vidhamunu thelpiti nindu jayinchu
Vaari bhaagyamu apajayamunu pondu vidhamuna
Delpiti neevetu nilchedavo{/lang-eng}

